<br>
Hence, I have gone through all the windows that I could and changed the background to &quot;tint&quot; and changed the tint color to 0/0/0 (which works much better); however, I have a few problems.<br>
<br>
1.  Some windows are textured no matter what, e.g. /bazaar /trader and the &quot;auto-equip&quot; section of the inventory screen.<br>
2.  I don't see any way to globally set background, so I had to do all the windows individually.<br>
<br>
